headline: Why Elevance Health (ELV) Stock Is Trading Lower Today
summary: Shares of health insurance provider Elevance Health (NYSE:EVH) fell 3.5% in the afternoon session after the company's CFO flagged potentially elevated medical costs and weakening margins at an investor conference.
